<p>A way with <code>data.table</code>, similar to what @tmfmnk showed</p>

<pre><code>library(data.table)
as.data.table(transpose(data))
#   V1 V2 V3 V4 V5
#1:  A  1  4  7 12
#2:  B  2  5  8 15
#3:  C  3  6  9 18
</code></pre>
